TITLE: Initializing ESLint Config (Flat)
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to initialize a basic ESLint configuration using the Flat Config style. It imports ESLint's recommended rules and TypeScript ESLint's recommended rules and combines them into a single configuration using the `tseslint.config` helper function.
SOURCE: https://github.com/typescript-eslint/typescript-eslint/blob/main/docs/users/Shared_Configurations.mdx#_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
// @ts-check

import eslint from '@eslint/js';
import tseslint from 'typescript-eslint';

export default tseslint.config(
  eslint.configs.recommended,
  tseslint.configs.recommended,
);
```

