TITLE: Project Configuration with tsconfig.json Path - JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Example of configuring the `project` option with a direct path to a `tsconfig.json` file. This tells the parser to use the specified TSConfig for type information.
SOURCE: https://github.com/typescript-eslint/typescript-eslint/blob/main/docs/packages/Parser.mdx#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: js
CODE:
```
project: './tsconfig.json';
```

