TITLE: Await Using (Correct Examples)
DESCRIPTION: This example shows the correct usage of `using` for synchronous disposables and `await using` for asynchronous disposables. It demonstrates the proper way to handle resources that need to be disposed of, whether synchronously or asynchronously, ensuring resources are released correctly.
