LANGUAGE: ts
CODE:
```
type Compute<A> = A extends Function ? A : { [K in keyof A]: Compute<A[K]> };
type Equal<X, Y> =
  (<T1>() => T1 extends Compute<X> ? 1 : 2) extends
    (<T2>() => T2 extends Compute<Y> ? 1 : 2)
  ? true
  : false;
```

