TITLE: Project Service Options Interface - TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Defines the interface `ProjectServiceOptions` for configuring the project service used by the parser. It includes options for allowing default project files, specifying a default TSConfig path, loading TypeScript plugins, and setting a maximum file match count for default projects.
