TITLE: createProgram Usage Example - JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use the `createProgram` function in JavaScript. It imports the typescript-estree library, calls `createProgram` to create a TypeScript program from a tsconfig file, and then uses the program with `parseAndGenerateServices` to parse code with type information.
